sequenceDiagram
    participant KFTO as Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>(PyTorchJob)
    participant EntryPt as accelerate_launch.py<br/>Container Entrypoint
    participant SFT as tuning.sft_trainer<br/>SFT Training Engine
    participant Data as tuning.data<br/>Data Pipeline
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC as PVC<br/>Persistent Volume
    participant GPU as GPU(s)<br/>CUDA/NCCL
    participant Tracker as Experiment Tracker<br/>(Aim/MLflow/ClearML)

    Note over KFTO,Tracker: Flow 1: SFT Training Job Execution

    KFTO->>EntryPt: Create Pod<br/>Config via env var (base64 JSON)<br/>or mounted config file
    EntryPt->>EntryPt: Parse config<br/>Determine num_processes<br/>Configure FSDP defaults
    EntryPt->>SFT: accelerate launch<br/>sft_trainer.train()

    SFT->>SFT: Parse JSON config<br/>→ dataclass hierarchy

    SFT->>HFHub: Download pre-trained model<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HFHub-->>SFT: Model weights (safetensors)

    SFT->>Data: Initialize data preprocessing
    Data->>Data: Auto-detect format<br/>(pretokenized/single-seq/<br/>chat/vision-multimodal)
    Data->>HFHub: Load dataset (if remote)<br/>HTTPS/443
    HFHub-->>Data: Dataset
    Data->>PVC: Load dataset (if local)
    PVC-->>Data: Dataset files
    Data->>Data: Apply DataHandler chain<br/>(map, filter, tokenize, collate)
    Data-->>SFT: Preprocessed dataset

    SFT->>SFT: Configure PEFT<br/>(LoRA/aLoRA/Prompt Tuning/<br/>GPTQ-LoRA/Full FT)
    SFT->>SFT: Optional: Load acceleration<br/>framework plugins

    SFT->>Tracker: Initialize tracker<br/>(file/aim/mlflow/clearml)

    Note over KFTO,Tracker: Flow 2: Multi-GPU FSDP Training

    SFT->>GPU: Begin training loop<br/>CUDA/NCCL
    loop Training Epochs
        GPU->>GPU: Forward pass
        GPU->>GPU: Backward pass
        GPU->>GPU: FSDP AllReduce/AllGather<br/>Port 29500/TCP (NCCL)
        GPU-->>SFT: Step metrics (loss, lr)
        SFT->>Tracker: Log metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
        SFT->>SFT: TrainerController<br/>evaluate rules<br/>(early stopping, etc.)
    end

    SFT->>PVC: Save model artifacts<br/>(checkpoints, final model)
    SFT->>PVC: Save PEFT adapters<br/>(if LoRA/aLoRA)

    alt Training Success
        SFT-->>EntryPt: Exit 0
        EntryPt-->>KFTO: Pod Succeeded
    else Training Failure
        SFT->>SFT: Write error to<br/>/dev/termination-log
        SFT-->>EntryPt: Exit 1
        EntryPt-->>KFTO: Pod Failed
    end
